actionConfiguration.body:
SELECT
  s.id,
  s.date,
  s.`custom code`,
  s.`product code`,
  s.`Piece-qtn`,  
  s.`piece-price`,
	(s.`Piece-qtn` * s.`piece-price`) AS total_price, 
  s.print,
  s.`sale code`,
  m.code,
  c.name
FROM `2020`.`saka` s
LEFT JOIN `2020`.`model` m
  ON s.`product code` = m.dcode
LEFT JOIN `2020`.`kaddname` c
  ON s.`custom code` = c.code
ORDER BY s.id DESC
LIMIT 10;
